A vintage 1960s-style technical illustration showing a cross-section of a complex mechanical device resembling a sleek desktop terminal, with interconnected gears, tubes, and modular components visible inside like an exploded engineering diagram. The machine has a retro-futuristic aesthetic with warm cream, burnt orange, and teal colors typical of mid-century technical manuals. Small figures in business attire examine different sections of the exposed machinery, pointing at various interconnected parts. The background features a subtle grid pattern on aged paper with slight yellowing at the edges. The composition suggests layers of technology working together harmoniously, conveying the concept of enterprise software architecture through analog visual metaphor.
